data.description: Step into your dream home, a modern masterpiece with a delightful touch of farmhouse charm. This property has undergone a meticulous top-to-bottom renovation, ensuring every detail exudes comfort, style, and a welcoming ambiance. The recent full remodel, completed within the last 5 years, makes this home truly turnkey, ready for you to settle in and start enjoying the best it has to offer.  Convenient RV access, addressing your storage needs with ease. Situated just minutes from Highway 80, parks, schools, shopping, and dining, this property effortlessly combines luxury living with everyday convenience. Your dream home awaits, where modern comfort and style meet the perfect location. Welcome to a lifestyle of ease and elegance.
